## Key Learnings
1. Idle scrambling is CRITICAL — disrupts Clips junctions
2. Junction discovery IS a bottleneck (19/65 at step 1000) but...
3. Explore-always hurts because it removes scramble pressure
4. TV7's explore/mine alternation is well balanced
5. Wide explore offsets (radius 30+) hurt — agents go too far
6. TV7/TV9 in tournament: 8.65 avg — big improvement over v348's 7.60
7. 2-agent games drag average down (ceiling ~6-7)
